[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-version effective dates and expiration dates     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-version sign-off records (IRB chair, principal   │
