[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ELIGIBILITY CRITERIA MODELING ─────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Per-trial criteria modeling]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Inclusion criteria: each criterion modeled as        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      structured predicate (or small predicate set) with   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      patient-facing question, deterministic evaluation    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      logic, expected data sources, confidence framing,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      records-confirmation-required flag                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Exclusion criteria: each criterion modeled the same  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      way                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Criteria with chart-data computability tagged for    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      cohort-matching (e.g., age, lab values, prior        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      diagnoses, prior medications)                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Criteria requiring patient self-report tagged for    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pre-screening conversation (e.g., current symptoms,  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      willingness to comply, willingness to travel)        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Criteria requiring records-based confirmation at     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      formal screening visit tagged accordingly (e.g.,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      central pathology review, specific imaging within    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      window, central molecular testing)                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-criterion clinical-research-leadership ownership │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      with named accountability                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Per-criterion version-controlled change history      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Outputs]                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pre-screening conversation flow (criteria suitable   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      for self-report ordered for conversational           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      delivery)                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cohort-matching predicate set (criteria suitable     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      for chart-data evaluation)                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Records-confirmation checklist (handed to            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordinator at handoff)                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Confidence-framing per criterion (this criterion is  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    312[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      strongly suggestive; this criterion requires         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    313[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      records-based confirmation)                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    314[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    316[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: per-trial structured eligibility model         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    317[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    suitable for conversational and structured             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    318[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    pre-screening]                                         │
