[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    537[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      recommendations beyond the trial, diagnosis-         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    538[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      attempted, treatment-recommendation-attempted,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    539[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      acute-symptom triage (recipe 11.6), mental-health    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    540[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      crisis (recipe 11.8), benefits questions about       │
