[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    568[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard output safety primitives from recipe 11.1]    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    569[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scope filter (no diagnosis; no clinical              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    570[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      recommendations beyond the trial; no informed-       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    571[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      consent collection; no protocol-deviation            │
