[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    573[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Vendor-managed guardrail layer                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    574[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Persona-and-tone check                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    575[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    576[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Recruitment-specific verification]                     │
