[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    582[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      contain coercive or undue-influence language; the    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    583[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      response does not over-emphasize benefits or         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    584[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      under-emphasize risks; the response acknowledges     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    585[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      patient choice; the response does not make           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    586[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      promises about specific outcomes)                    │
