[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    616[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-stated logistical context (transportation,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    617[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      time availability, accompanying caregiver, language  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    618[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      needs)                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    619[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Likely-eligibility result with confidence framing    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    620[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Records-confirmation checklist (criteria flagged     │
