[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    726[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sampled clinical-research-quality review]              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    727[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Random sample plus targeted sample of low-           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    728[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      confidence pre-screens, persuasive-pattern flags,    │
