[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    733[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      modes (out-of-scope, off-IRB-material, persuasive-   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    734[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pattern, consent-boundary-violation, criterion-      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    735[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      misinterpretation, equity-disparity)                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    736[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - IRB-material and criteria-model revisions driven     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    737[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      by review findings with clinical-research-           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    738[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      leadership and IRB sign-off                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    739[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
